contract.task_intent: Convert string to URL-friendly slug format
contract.prompt: Write a Python function called 'slugify' that takes a string and converts it to a URL-friendly slug. Convert to lowercase, replace spaces with hyphens, and remove special characters except hyphens.

assignments.text: Call(func=Attribute(value=Name(id='re', ctx=Load()), attr='sub', ctx=Load()), args=[Constant(value='[\\s]+'), Constant(value='-'), Name(id='text', ctx=Load())])

llm_results.raw_output:
def slugify(text):
    import re
    text = text.lower()
    text = re.sub(r'[^a-z0-9\s-]', '', text)
    text = re.sub(r'[\s-]+', '-', text).strip('-')
    return text
